Name: Eetcafé La Chambre
Review Text: This is a Very Cute little local café. Cozy interior and outdoor seating area. Friendly service. The doggie was so friendly. The quick bites were really nice. The steaks were good but a little dry, but the good service provided makes up for it.

Name: Eetcafé La Chambre
Review Text: Cute little local café. Cozy interior and outdoor seating area. Heineken on tap and some bottled Belgian beers. Friendly service.
